                    <value>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Hi {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;I&amp;#39;m Heidi Rubio! I&amp;#39;m thrilled to introduce myself as your new Wellness Concierge at 10X Health! I&amp;#39;m here to provide you with exceptional support and ensure a seamless, high quality experience throughout your wellness journey.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;A little about me:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif&quot;&gt;I am a passionate professional with over 8 years of experience in integrative wellness and aesthetics, specializing in functional medicine and patient care. Fluent in both English and Spanish, I focus on educating patients and serving as a supportive mentor throughout their journey to optimal health. My dedication to excellence and expertise in the field have allowed me to thrive as a highly respected Concierge at 10X Health.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;I am dedicated to understanding your unique needs and collaborating with your care team to deliver the precise, personalized care you deserve. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;If you have any questions or feedback, don&amp;#39;t hesitate to reach out. I&amp;#39;m here to help elevate your wellness experience every step of the way! I look forward to working with you and helping optimize your wellness journey.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Feel free to book a call with me&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://calendly.com/hrubio-3/10x-health-vip-check-in&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;HERE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;In health,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</value>
